metadata.name: ธ
metadata.description:
ธ is the first alphabet of the word “ธรรม” (dharma) which represented here as truth. At first, while we are in delight and holding on it. We think it is real and hope for eternal. However, it is actually an illusion. We obsess and enjoy with senses, feel like dancing with the world. It is only celebrating with illusion.

Technique: fingerprint stamp
